Arrow Function

This was added in JS in ES6

An arroe function is simply a special form of function expression that is shorter and therefore faster to writer.

Syntax

// arrow function 

birthyear => 2037 - birthyear ;

EXAMPLE :

const calcage3 = birthyear => 2037 - birthyear ;

const age3 = calcage3(2006);

console.log(age3);










